    "English": "A shifting vortex of <span class=\"name name-special\">atlantideum</span>, attuned to the growing collective will housed inside Nada's <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Prime Terminal</span>. Current sentience threshold: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">??%</span>.<br><br>The grains oscillate in a pattern, but the message is unintelligible.",
